configuration.models.custom.description:
Configure custom language models for each provider. These models will be used instead of retrieving the model listing from the provider.

**Note:** This setting does not affect GitHub Copilot models.

Use provider IDs as keys, with arrays of model configurations as values.

Example:
```json
{
  "anthropic-api": [
    {
      "name": "Claude Sonnet 4.5", // required: display name
      "identifier": "claude-sonnet-4-5", // required: API model ID
      "maxInputTokens": 200000, // optional: input token limit
      "maxOutputTokens": 8192 // optional: output token limit
    }
  ]
}
```
